itempriceusddefault_maxtofixed2 sale itempriceusddefaulttofixed2   itempriceusddefault_maxtofixed2 how do you sublimate award ribbons sublimating award ribbons involves a few key steps design preparation create your design using graphic software ensure its mirrored and printed with sublimation ink on sublimation paper heat press setup preheat your heat press to the recommended temperature for sublimation usually around 385400f 196204c prepare the ribbon cut your polyester ribbon to the desired length place it on the heat press ensuring its flat and smooth position the design lay the printed sublimation paper on the ribbon with the ink side facing down pressing cover with a teflon sheet or parchment paper to protect the ribbon and press the pressing time typically ranges from 3060 seconds cool and peel after pressing remove the ribbon and let it cool gently peel off the paper to reveal the sublimated design finishing touches if needed trim any excess material or add any additional hardware like pins or clips always test your process on a scrap piece of ribbon to finetune temperature pressure and time settings for the best results do polyester award ribbons tear polyester award ribbons are generally quite durable and resistant to tearing under normal use polyester as a synthetic fabric has inherent strength and flexibility making it less prone to tearing compared to many natural fibers however like any material they can tear if subjected to excessive force or sharp objects proper handling and storage can help in maintaining their condition over time in typical scenarios like award ceremonies display or light handling polyester ribbons should hold up well without tearing what are custom sublimated award ribbons and medals best for custom sublimated award ribbons and medals are ideal for a variety of events where personalized vibrant and detailed awards are desired they are perfect for sports tournaments academic competitions corporate recognition programs community events and personal celebrations the sublimation process allows for incorporating specific logos texts and colors making these awards highly customizable this results in unique and memorable keepsakes that are both visually appealing and durable capable of preserving the significance of achievements and special moments their versatility and quality make them suitable
